{"tid":742360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滬深交易所稱「同股不同權」垃圾股票暫不納入港股通買賣範圍","createTime":"2018-07-14T13:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T13:56:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e29bd0e12a5c6a6b806ca56466646bbb02c075","tid":742360,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"支那也不屌既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1406987_1_L_20180714172943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1406987_1_L_20180714172943.jpg&h=6c885130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滬深交易所宣布，同股不同權架構，暫時不會納入滬港通與深港通下的港股通股票範圍，由7月16日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n滬深交易所表示，自2018年7月16日起，恒生綜合大型股指數、恒生綜合中型股指數、恒生綜合小型股指數的成份股中，屬於外國公司股票、合訂證券、不同投票權架構公司股票，暫不納入滬港通和深港通下的港股通股票範圍，其他股票調入調出正常進行。<br />\n<br />\n🇨🇳🇨🇳內地🇨🇳🇨🇳傳媒估計，這項宣布顯示，7月9日在香港上市，實行同股不同權架構的☭☭小米☭☭集團，暫時無法納入港股通範圍。"},{"pid":"1dda1cd4b6b3bf6840284510668aeb25d59adc3e","tid":742360,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"即係屌米係揾香港人笨"},{"pid":"e5dda28c4d17a5c31e6a8e24219f002c5ec45939","tid":742360,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1dda1cd4b6b3bf6840284510668aeb25d59adc3e","tid":742360,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"即係屌米係揾香港人笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"擺到明"},{"pid":"2c6b470420d7aefeb9812b062c4dc563ba93f963","tid":742360,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1dda1cd4b6b3bf6840284510668aeb25d59adc3e","tid":742360,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"即係屌米係揾香港人笨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"多撚謝 777 同李屌加<img sr